  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "This Project intends to support the addition of transmission capacity to the intigrated power system, and to provide access to electricity and cooking fuel to communities in the area  of the Kabeli 132 kV transmission line.The project consists of the following three parts:\r\n1. Kabeli Corridor 132 kV Transmission Line,\r\n2. Community - based Rural Electrification-Grid Extension, and\r\n3. Rural Enhanced Energy Services."
